2026-05-08T00:43:17.2016327Z 22    <!--
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2016770Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2017324Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2017843Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2018489Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2019128Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2019754Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2020393Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2021228Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2021855Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2022446Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-08T00:43:17.2022910Z 33    -->
